@node Introduction "Connectix Cam as Webcam ON Amiga V1.0 - Introduction"
@next Requirements
@prev TOC
@help HelpPage
@font XEN.font 11

@{b}Introduction:@{ub}

Welcome to THe Connectix Quickcam as a Webcam For amiga How to Guide.

In here I hope to help any of you Fortunate to have obtained a camera

through Tony Phillipson to get it to Work as a webcam .

2 years ago I bought his adapter and a camera to go with it . It has

Been a long road to getting this cam Actually working as a webcam .

The final Breakthrough was a prg called Sgrab . 

I have to thank my Friend Paul Denmark for Putting up with me these 

last 2 years and for making the arexx scripts for the cam . Without 

him this really wouldnt have happened .

 @{"Read On" link Requirements}

@endnode
