@{b}Requirements:@{ub}

Hardware Requirements

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  Connectix Quick cam and Adapter (listed in the where to get area of this doc)

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  An Amiga with Working Disk Drive Port

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  68030 33 Mhz +


What you need for this program to operate fully:

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  Sgrab.lha (Available at Aminet)

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  jpeglibrary40.lha (Available At aminet)

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  FTPMount_1_0.lha (Also at Aminet)

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  FTPMount_upd.lha (Also at Aminet)

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  Rexxmast running in the the back Ground


Suggested extras:

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  68040 or faster

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  AGA system

@{fg highlight}-@{fg text}  3.1+ Amiga OS

